{"tid":2058101,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄧炳強先生我又有野同你講啦","createTime":"2020-06-10T02:10:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T02:48:44.000Z","uid":220066,"like":45,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0f301de60ec59d50e4ce46333f2badb5defb0765","tid":2058101,"uid":220066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T02:10:26.000Z","msg":"我之前開post罵你<br />\n之後一個禮拜就派人跟蹤我<br />\n甚至乎無啦啦要查我身份證<br />\n你班同事查我果陣幾激動架喎<br />\n睇嚟我罵你嘅野真係罵岩得幾岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實學你話齋行得正企得正洗乜驚<br />\n睇嚟你都幾驚一個普通市民去話你<br />\n所以有傳你買武器去射手足<br />\n等佢地手手腳腳永久殘廢<br />\n咁你都幾叻叻豬喎<br />\n你知唔知你好快會到聯合國受審<br />\n唔知你心情又如何呢<br />\n我正係知你同果班三萬有牌恐怖分子<br />\n同埋721白衫人都會被美國制裁<br />\n至於大波廢老好似美國都有資產喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你放心啦而家唔止香港人想招呼你<br />\n而係全球都好想招呼你地想同你地交流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以你犯法就係犯法一定要負責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb649448bfece004593c7c0b99e3ad8c082ccaf2","tid":2058101,"uid":220066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T02:12:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"43f7e0c222f740ff1ec0e9050efa428c8b69e4f7","tid":2058101,"uid":114014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T02:13:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8ce5105161b6bd3e288d054ecb8b908563a9811","tid":2058101,"uid":58209,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T02:14:10.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪有精神病？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78bf2fe4a5438b3d0b737d9ba6d5efb1f467ac80","tid":2058101,"uid":299991,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0f301de60ec59d50e4ce46333f2badb5defb0765","tid":2058101,"uid":220066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T02:10:26.000Z","msg":"我之前開post罵你<br